# FaceConnect — MQTT ACL
# Format:  user <username>
#          topic <read|write|readwrite|deny> <topic>
#
# Topic convention:
#   devices/<device-id>/cmd    — gateway sends commands to device
#   devices/<device-id>/status — device reports state to gateway

# Gateway service — full access to all device topics
user gateway
topic readwrite devices/#
topic readwrite status/#

# Phase 2: add per-device credentials below
# Each device can only touch its own topics — limits blast radius if compromised.
#
# user lock-01
# topic read  devices/lock-01/cmd
# topic write devices/lock-01/status
#
# user lights-01
# topic read  devices/lights-01/cmd
# topic write devices/lights-01/status
